data.description: EAST ORLANDO PROPERTY!! ! The established neighborhood has optional HOA fee and is conveniently located near to the 408, 417, and Florida Hospital East. BRAND-NEW Roof & AC and a cozy fireplace. The kitchen equipped with granite counters top and an abundance of cabinetry flows into the dining room. There is plenty of space for all your needs with two stories of living space. Split bedroom floor-plan features the downstairs master bedroom with dual closets and an en suite bathroom. UNIQUE BONUS ROOM upstairs is perfect for entertaining offering a wet bar and French door access to the second story screened in patio over the garage with a spiral staircase leading to the sparkling swimming pool and spa in the brick paved screened in lanai. Attractive and long lasting tile roof adds to the curb appeal. **IDEAL LOCATION!** The University of Central Florida or downtown Orlando are only 15 minutes away. Located less than 15 minutes to shopping, dining, and entertainment in the Waterford Lakes Town Center.  SELLER OFFER 5K CONCESSION CREDIT TOWARDS AT CLOSING TIME.
